  * ubiquity-bluetooth-agent: Don't touch /tmp/ubiquity-bluetooth-done
    if the file already exists. (LP: #951402)
  * gtk-ui: Drop poke_screensaver and replace by code disabling it in
    gsettings. (LP: #951336)
